Product name: Steiff hand puppet fox Smardy, vintage 1965 - 1978, red mohair fox with tail, vintage animal glove puppet, old puppet theatre fox doll
Description:
Steiff hand puppet fox Smardy, vintage 1965 - 1978, red mohair fox with tail, vintage animal glove puppet, old puppet theatre fox doll
Here is a very cute & smart Steiff hand puppet fox complete with a beautiful bushy fox tail! His name is Smardy, he is a crafty fox out of an arithmetic book of the same name for children. Our vintage animal glove puppet was produced from 1965 to 1976. Old Steiff fox hand puppet is made of red, white & black mohair with plastic eyes. Fox’ head is stuffed with wood wool (excelsior), the sheath for the puppet player’s finger is made of plastics. Vintage Steiff hand – fox lost his chest tag, ear button & yellow Steiff label.
Old Steiff Hand - Fox measures 17 cm / 6 ¾ inches – glove only (fits to every normal sized adult hand) & 25 cm / 10 inches to his head without ears & tail.
Our cute vintage Steiff Fox Smardy hand puppet is in very good vintage condition as you can see in the photographs!
Old Steiff Hand - Fox is a real eye candy for the Steiff or shabby vintage toy collector; they are really very rare to find nowadays due to the very short time & limited number of their production!
We do have a whole puppet theatre of vintage hand puppets listed here: 
www.etsy.com/shop/ShabbyGoesLucky?ref=l2-shopheader-name&section_id=13654244
There is another vintage Steiff hand – fox among them: 
www.etsy.com/listing/261171177/steiff-hand-fox-vintage-1952-1963-hand?ref=shop_home_active_8
***Please notice: This vintage Steiff animal puppet belongs not into the hands of children; it may not fulfil the safety standards for toys in our time! So it is not meant as a toy, though a collector’s & vintage toy lover’s item only for display & decoration only! 
***Steiff mohair Hand – Fox comes without the stand that is to be seen in the photographs!
We will ship all items insured on Priority mail.

Product name: Tibetan ring Filigree ring Handcrafted ring Ethnic ring Boho ring Gypsy ring Buddhist ring Amulet ring Tribal ring Gift for her Gift for him
Description:
Tibetan Jewellery is also known as Buddhist jewellery or Himalayan jewellery. Jewellery plays an important role in the culture of Tibet. Jewellery is a part of dress, a symbol of spirituality, and a part of everyday life. Jewellery also has the properties of an amulet, bring protection from evil spirits to the wearer.
The filigree design is achieved by hand weaving silver threads using traditional tools and techniques, creating a unique braided effect.
Material: Brass
Size: Best fit US ring size 8-10 (UK: P1/2 – T1/2) but can adjust to other size.
Width: 1.8cm(0.7")
Please note it is a vintage item which is completely handcrafted, so minor imperfections are present. It's the way it's made and I personally think adds to the charm. Please enlarge the photos to see the details. 
*PACKAGING*
This ring will come with a quality jewellery box in natural colour and ready to give as a gift. 
*SHIPPING INFORMATION*
UNITED KINGDOM
I use First Class Royal Mail for deliveries within the UK. According to Royal Mail, delivery aim is 1-3 working days. For additional security you can add First Class Signe shipping upgrade at checkout.
ALL OTHER COUNTRIES
I use International standard Air Mail to all the European countries, plus Australia, Canada, Japan, New Zealand, Russia and United States. There is NO TRACKING NUMBER with this service. Please add the International Tracked and Signed shipping upgrade at checkout if you need additional security.
For the rest of the countries in the world, I only use International Tracked and (or) Signed shipping. The standard shipping for these countries are Tracked and (or) Signed. 
According to Royal Mail, for European Countries delivery aim is 3-7 working days. For the countries outside of Europe, delivery aim is 5-10 working days. Please note the above are Royal Mail aimed delivery times. Weather conditions, custom control and other unexpected factors might delay shipping. 
*RETURNS & EXCHANGES*
I really hope you are fully satisfied with your purchase, but if for any reason you are not please contact me first via Etsy conversations. I will do my best to resolve any issues as I believe all the issues can be resoled in a positive way. Returns and Exchanges will be happily accepted. Just contact me within 14 days of delivery.

Product name: Chung King Express 50 Vintage Premium Chinese Postage Stamps Peoples Republic of China PRC Taiwan Cantonese Mandarin Asia Han Formosa Red
Description:
Up from the 36th chamber!  In case you didn't already know, the People's Republic of China (中华人民共和国 / Zhōnghuá Rénmín Gònghéguó) has the largest population in the world and some of the most collectible philately in the world too!  Who can resist the beautiful Chinese characters and historic images on these stamps?  Many feature beautiful traditional Chinese artwork, first created during the ancient dynasties.  This colorful collection features 50 postage stamps from the late 1800s through the 20th century (although mostly pre-1980s) handpicked by your very own Head Asian In Charge (that's me).  
All of these stamps are off paper or MNH.  Some are cancelled with historic postmarks from all around the mainland (PRC), Indochina and Taiwan (Formosa) and some are uncancelled, never hinged and in mint condition.  Favored by philatelists worldwide, many of these stamps retain high values, even after cancellation. This is a premium collection containing used Junk issues and a few early PRC MNH issues.  There may be some minor imperfections but they only add authentic antique character; overall these are in outstanding condition!  
Not only can these stamps be appreciated by philatelic collectors & enthusiasts, they can also be used for decorative paper crafting, card making, collages, scrapbooking, journaling, jewelry making and more!  Sorting an organizing stamps offers endless hours of soothing relaxation for both the young and old. Getting your kids into stamps at a young age will help them to be better organized in the future.
If you are looking for something in particular please convo me for me details on a custom order.

Product name: Large Wall Stencil Acanthus Trellis Allover Stencil Great Alternatiive to Wall Decals and Wallpaper for Wall Decor
Description:
A modern trellis wall stencil pattern. Simple and elegant and perfect for quickly stenciling a wallpaper effect on a feature wall or whole room. Try stenciling with metallic paints for a dramatic effect!
3088L Large Acanthus Trellis Allover Stencil
Actual Design Size: 20.5" w x 26.5" h, Reusable 10 mil mylar
Decorating with stencils is fast, fun, and easy! Our durable 10mil mylar stencils are designed to be used repeatedly from an easy-to-clean material.
Stenciled Wall Décor: Use stencils for personalized wall decoration by simply adding in the paint colors of your choice using a stencil brush or stencil rollers. 
Wall stencil patterns include allover damask stencils, motif stencils, and border stencils. You can mix and match stencil designs to create a unique decorating scheme that fits your style and your space.
Stenciling on Fabric: Use stencil fabric paints or simply add Textile Medium (available at the craft store) to any acrylic paint to make it suitable for fabric stenciling. Use stencils on tablecloths, curtains, pillows, placemats, and more.
Stencils on Furniture: Stencils are ideal for adding pattern to almost any hard surface, including furniture. Transform a tabletop, chest of drawers, or cabinet door with paint and stencils. Protect stenciled furniture with multiple coats of water-based varnish to protect your stencil art from normal wear and tear.
For more tips and ideas on using stencils and detailed stencil instruction, see our website at: http://www.royaldesignstudio.com
Our Stencil History: Royal Design Studio was founded in 1994 by renowned stencil artist and innovator Melanie Royals. Since then, we have been creating and developing unique stencils and stencil application techniques for DIYers and professional stencil artisans alike. We are very excited to see another resurgence in interest in stencil art for wall décor, and are very happy to share our stencils and ideas for stenciling with you!
©Copyright 2011 Royal Design Studio

Product name: Aluminium good luck token/charm/pocket token/promise token/motivational coin. Personalised with a message or quote of your choice.
Description:
Aluminium good luck token/charm/pocket token/promise token/motivational coin. Personalised with a message, quote, memorable date or image of your choice.
This aluminium circle makes a beautifully unique love token/pocket token, have a message for your loved one stamped onto it, they can carry this with them always.
The circle is just over 2.5cm wide, is 14g, 1.6mm thick aluminium, meaning it can be stamped on both sides.
Your token will arrive in a 5x7cm organza gift bag, ready to give as a present. 
~Text options ~ 
Unless you request a specific font, I will select the font I feel is most suitable for your piece.
To see a comparison image of all of the font options, please view the photos for this listing: 
https://www.etsy.com/uk/listing/182399359/aluminium-hand-stamped-credit-card-size
Typewriter is basic and clear 2mm font, which allows me to stamp the maximum number of characters onto each piece.
Jenna Sue is a 3 & 2.5mm font, very slightly italic, whilst remaining clear and stylish.
Fornax is a 2mm cursive and beautifully elegant font. Fornax is great for use with quotes or poems, to emphasise words within a block of text or to sign a name.
Sculptor is a 3mm uppercase fancy block font, it looks great when used to emphasise certain words in a line/paragraph of text.
Lollipop is a quirky uppercase 4mm font.
Kids print is a 3 & 4 mm font, which mimics the handwriting of a young child. Kids print is perfect for a message to parents/grandparents from children or to sign a name. Due to the larger size of this text it is not suitable for all pieces, and may require a shorter message. 
Large typewriter  is a 6mm upper and lower case font, used for single initials or to begin a word, the large typewriter font looks great combined with the 2mm sized typewriter font.
* PLEASE READ THE FOLLOWING INFORMATION *
By purchasing an item from Apple of my eye, you are agreeing that you have read the full item description.
Please view my shop section 'add on items' to find gift boxes and additional options for customising your piece. 
Please let me know exactly what you'd like stamping on to your piece in the "notes to seller" section whilst completing you purchase. If you are unsure whether you chosen text will fit onto the shape just send me a message and ill double check for you. If you do not send personalisation with your order, I will contact you once to request personalisation, then unfortunately I will have to cancel the order.
To view my full collection of hand stamped metal, please search Apple of my eye jewellery and gifts on Face book or follow me on instagram lisa.bramley.
Where one aluminium shape is stacked on top of another, over a period of time you will notice very slight wear under the top piece.
Each Individual letter/image is stamped by hand, the letters may not be in perfect alignment. Wherever a letter is stamped, this very slightly changes the appearance of the aluminium on the reverse side of the piece, this in no way takes away from the beauty of the piece and they look great stamped on both sides. 
Please have a look at my pictures which show this clearly. Personally I love the handmade vs mass produced look and feel it makes each piece truly unique.
I work with only the highest quality, food safe, hypoallergenic aluminium.
Aluminium is a lightweight metal, making it perfect for use in jewellery, it is silver in colour all the way through and will not tarnish or change colour when cared for correctly.
Due to the space on each blank, it is not always possible to stamp the text in the exact positioning of your order. I will always stamp the pieces to ensure that they look their best. Due to the volume of orders I receive it is not always possible to contact the buyer before stamping the piece.
